OL,3,CBurnley worker left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after being 'crushed' at work
OL,6,FA waste and recycling company has been
OL,7,Ffined after an employee suffered life-
OL,8,Fchanging injuries when he was crushed
OL,9,Fby a reversing heavy lifting vehicle.
OL,11,FJordan Campion, from Burnley, was
OL,12,Fworking for Sheridan Skips Burnley
OL,13,FLimited at its site in Smiths Yard,
OL,14,FClifton Street, when the incident
OL,15,Foccurred on 12 March 2024.
OL,17,FNow 21, he and three other employees
OL,18,Fwere sorting and separating waste
OL,19,Fmaterial by hand in the same yard as a
OL,20,Fcolleague operating a telehandler.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
