OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773644653
OL,3,CBurnley worker left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after being 'crushed' at work
OL,6,FMr Campion was standing against a
OL,7,Fbrick wall at the side of the yard
OL,8,Fwhen the telehandler reversed into
OL,9,Fhim, crushing him against the wall.
OL,11,FAs a result, he suffered multiple
OL,12,Ffractures, nerve damage to his right
OL,13,Farm and internal organ injuries. He
OL,14,Falso lost partial hearing in his right
OL,15,Fear and developed a blood clot which
OL,16,Fcaused optical damage to his right
OL,17,Feye, resulting in permanent sight loss
OL,18,Fin that eye.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773644653
OL,3,CBurnley worker left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after being 'crushed' at work
OL,6,FAn HSE investigation found that
OL,7,Femployees frequently worked in the
OL,8,Fyard while vehicles operated alongside
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,FSheridan Skips Burnley Limited had not
OL,12,Fundertaken a suitable and sufficient
OL,13,Frisk assessment and failed to provide
OL,14,Fadequate measures for the safe
OL,15,Fsegregation of vehicles and
OL,16,Fpedestrians.
OL,18,FThere was no physical protection from
OL,19,Fvehicle movement, which regularly put
OL,20,Femployees in considerable danger.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773644653
OL,3,CBurnley worker left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after being 'crushed' at work
OL,6,FThe investigation also found that the
OL,7,Ftelehandler operator could not see
OL,8,Fclearly while reversing, as the
OL,9,Fmachine was missing mirrors to aid
OL,10,Freversing ` a deficiency the company
OL,11,Fhad failed to address.
OL,13,FMr Campion was in hospital for nearly
OL,14,Ftwo weeks following the incident.
OL,16,FIn his victim personal statement, Mr
OL,17,FCampion said: "My incident has caused
OL,18,Fmy family great distress. They
OL,19,Fpermanently worry about me; they never
OL,20,Fthought that I wouldn't be safe in
OL,21,Fwork."
OL,26,@yD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773644653
OL,3,CBurnley worker left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after being 'crushed' at work
OL,6,F" They say you never expect to see
OL,7,Fyour child go off to work and to get a
OL,8,Fphone call to say that they have had
OL,9,Fan incident and might not survive."
OL,11,FSheridan Skips Burnley Limited, of
OL,12,FCathedral Gates, Manchester, pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to breaching Section 2(1) of
OL,14,Fthe Health and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,15,F1974.
OL,17,FThe company was fined #24,000 and
OL,18,Fordered to pay #4,777 in costs at
OL,19,FBlackburn Magistrates' Court on
OL,20,FWednesday 11 March 2026.
OL,26,@qD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
