FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773644653
OL,3,CBurnley worker left with life-changing
OL,4,Cinjuries after being 'crushed' at work
OL,6,FAfter the hearing, HSE inspector
OL,7,FAnthony Banks said: "This young man's
OL,8,Finjuries could so easily have been
OL,9,Favoided with the implementation of
OL,10,Fsafe working practices, including
OL,11,Fpedestrian and vehicle segregation and
OL,12,Fsafe refuges for workers whilst
OL,13,Fvehicles were operating.
OL,15,F"This should serve as a reminder to
OL,16,Fbusinesses operating in the waste
OL,17,Findustry to ensure that workplace
OL,18,Ftransport is appropriately considered,
OL,19,Fwith control measures introduced to
OL,20,Fensure the appropriate separation of
OL,21,Fvehicles and pedestrians."
OL,26,@oD@UOUwD@AOU}D@ZO]
